lyr_name: Layer name (choose from dropdown or enter new layer)

inc_moisture_type: Was sample rewetted or measured directly from field?

inc_fraction_modern_sd: Incubation Fraction Modern Standard Deviation (sample; If replicates reported with mean value only)
